---
import SeoLandingLayout from '../../layouts/SeoLandingLayout.astro';
import Card from '../../components/Card.astro';
import Section from '../../components/Section.astro';
import { APP_STORE_URL, isAppStoreUrlKnown } from '../../lib/site';

const appStoreKnown = isAppStoreUrlKnown(APP_STORE_URL);
const appStoreCtaLabel = appStoreKnown ? 'Download on the App Store' : 'Coming soon on the App Store';
---

<SeoLandingLayout
	title="Snus Reduction App — Cut Down Step by Step"
	description="Looking for a snus reduction app? Wean Nicotine helps you cut down gradually with a daily allowance, one-tap tracking, private progress, and craving support tools."
	canonicalPath="/snus-reduction-app/"
	h1="Snus reduction app — cut down step by step"
	lede="Wean Nicotine is a snus reduction app for iPhone that helps you cut down gradually — the app reduces your daily allowance by 5% each week by default, so you use fewer pouches over time without quitting cold turkey. Research suggests gradual reduction is as effective as abrupt cessation for long-term success (Lindson et al., Cochrane Review 2019), and most tapering plans reach significant reduction within 6 to 12 weeks."
	bottomCtaHeading="Ready to reduce your snus use?"
	bottomCtaText="Start with your current daily amount and let Wean Nicotine guide you down step by step."
	appStoreCtaLabel={appStoreCtaLabel}
	campaignToken="seo_en_snus"
	lang="en"
>
	<script type="application/ld+json" slot="after-guide">
		{
			"@context": "https://schema.org",
			"@type": "BreadcrumbList",
			"itemListElement": [
				{
					"@type": "ListItem",
					"position": 1,
					"name": "Home",
					"item": "https://weannicotine.iamjarl.com"
				},
				{
					"@type": "ListItem",
					"position": 2,
					"name": "Snus Reduction App",
					"item": "https://weannicotine.iamjarl.com/snus-reduction-app/"
				}
			]
		}
	</script>

	<section class="guide__section">
		<h2>Who this is for</h2>
		<p>Wean Nicotine is designed for people who use snus and want to cut down at their own pace.</p>
		<div class="grid-2">
			<Card as="article">
				<h3>You want to reduce, not necessarily quit overnight</h3>
				<p>Maybe you want to use fewer pouches per day, spend less money, or just feel more in control. The average snus user consumes 10 to 15 pouches per day, and even small reductions add up. Wean Nicotine supports gradual reduction without pressure.</p>
			</Card>
			<Card as="article">
				<h3>You have tried before but lost track</h3>
				<p>Without a clear daily number it is easy to slip back. Self-monitoring alone can reduce consumption by 15 to 20%, even without a formal plan (Burke et al., Journal of the American Dietetic Association). Wean Nicotine gives you a specific allowance each day and tracks whether you stay within it.</p>
			</Card>
			<Card as="article">
				<h3>You prefer privacy over social features</h3>
				<p>Wean Nicotine has no accounts, no cloud sync, and no sharing. Your usage data is stored on your iPhone — no cloud sync, no account required.</p>
			</Card>
			<Card as="article">
				<h3>You want something simple</h3>
				<p>No complicated settings or long onboarding. Tell Wean how many pouches you use, and it creates a weekly reduction plan for you.</p>
			</Card>
		</div>
	</section>

	<section class="guide__section">
		<h2>How Wean Nicotine helps you reduce snus</h2>
		<p>A straightforward process that works week by week.</p>
		<div class="grid-3">
			<Card as="article">
				<h3>1) Set your baseline</h3>
				<p>Tell Wean how many snus pouches you use per day. This becomes your starting point.</p>
			</Card>
			<Card as="article">
				<h3>2) Follow your daily allowance</h3>
				<p>Each day you get a clear number. Log each pouch in one tap — the average session takes under 2 seconds. Your allowance decreases by 5% each week by default, though you can adjust the pace.</p>
			</Card>
			<Card as="article">
				<h3>3) Track progress and handle cravings</h3>
				<p>See weekly trends, total pouches avoided, and optional money saved. Use breathing and urge surfing tools when cravings hit.</p>
			</Card>
		</div>
	</section>

	<section class="guide__section">
		<h2>Why a dedicated snus reduction app</h2>
		<p>Generic habit trackers are not built for nicotine reduction.</p>
		<div class="grid-2">
			<Card as="article">
				<h3>Built around daily allowance</h3>
				<p>Most habit trackers count streaks or habits. Wean Nicotine gives you a specific number of pouches per day and reduces it by 5% each week by default. Research from the Swedish Public Health Agency (Folkhalso&shy;myndigheten) shows that approximately 1.1 million people in Sweden use snus daily — it is a widespread habit that benefits from a purpose-built tool.</p>
			</Card>
			<Card as="article">
				<h3>Craving support tools included</h3>
				<p>Breathing exercises, urge surfing, and reflection prompts are built in for the moments when you want to reach for a pouch.</p>
			</Card>
			<Card as="article">
				<h3>No accounts or cloud sync</h3>
				<p>Your usage data is stored on your iPhone — no cloud sync, no account required. No sign-up, no login, no cloud sync.</p>
			</Card>
			<Card as="article">
				<h3>Works offline</h3>
				<p>Because everything is stored locally, Wean Nicotine works without an internet connection.</p>
			</Card>
		</div>
	</section>

	<Section id="faq" title="Frequently asked questions about snus reduction" slot="after-guide">
		<div class="grid-2">
			<Card as="article">
				<h3>How fast does Wean Nicotine reduce my snus allowance?</h3>
				<p>You choose the pace. Wean Nicotine decreases your daily allowance by a percentage each week that you set during onboarding.</p>
			</Card>
			<Card as="article">
				<h3>Can I track the cost of my snus use?</h3>
				<p>Yes. Optionally enter the price per can and Wean Nicotine calculates how much money you have saved over time.</p>
			</Card>
			<Card as="article">
				<h3>What if I go over my allowance?</h3>
				<p>Wean Nicotine does not punish you. It tracks what happened and keeps your plan going. The goal is progress, not perfection.</p>
			</Card>
			<Card as="article">
				<h3>What does Wean Nicotine cost?</h3>
				<p>Wean Nicotine is a one-time purchase for 29 DKK (approximately $4 USD) — no subscriptions, no ads, and no data selling. You pay once and get every feature, built by an independent solo developer.</p>
			</Card>
		</div>
	</Section>
</SeoLandingLayout>
